{"tid":2368323,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"藍可兒離奇命案 拍成四集紀錄片下月Netflix上架","createTime":"2021-01-16T05:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T05:43:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"66f209fe3aadda396bc3334497bf929e471e79db","tid":2368323,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210116/CPQRRS76LZGVZGCZJ64RFNOELM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210116%2FCPQRRS76LZGVZGCZJ64RFNOELM%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=ab916197\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210116%2FCPQRRS76LZGVZGCZJ64RFNOELM%2F&h=d677b0d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210116/CPQRRS76LZGVZGCZJ64RFNOELM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n藍可兒離奇命案 拍成四集紀錄片下月Netflix上架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uo5iBdUFRzvwtW9ju1DeVRwQsK0=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U2CPAS4DTFAZLIVG5C7PVBAOTI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fuo5iBdUFRzvwtW9ju1DeVRwQsK0%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU2CPAS4DTFAZLIVG5C7PVBAOTI.jpg&h=b88c0702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大港裔女生藍可兒，2013年被發現離奇死於洛杉磯塞西爾酒店（Cecil Hotel）的天台水缸，事件當年轟動全球，由於相隔八年仍是疑點重重，Netflix宣佈把這個詭異事件拍成一共四集的犯罪紀錄片《Crime Scene: The Vanishing at The Cecil Hotel》，安排2月10日起上架。<br />\n<br />\n藍可兒死亡事件發生在2013年1月底，當時21歲的藍可兒隻身到洛杉磯旅遊，入住塞西爾酒店，五天後離奇失蹤。警方曾公開一段升降機閉路電視片段，見到藍可兒行徑古怪，一時躲在升降機角落，一時似與升降機外的其他人談話，直至2月19日，有酒店住客投訴水壓有問題，始發現藍可兒全裸陳屍在酒店天台水缸。<br />\n<br />\n雖然藍可兒的死因眾說紛紜，驗屍官推斷她是死於「意外」，奈何此案疑團太多，警方最後認為無案可查已終止調查，最後成了世紀懸案。多年來，各地曾以藍可兒之死作為電影題材，整件事更被恐怖傳聞及神秘氣氛包圍，今次的四集紀錄片會解構出事地點的環境，並訪問調查人員、酒店員工、其他住客，望還原出事件的真相。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/c0sV7MFQpbycp94Klk5Z0fLZIFo=/1200x628/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NOIC33HGAJFMDE3LYIJLZP6UOQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fc0sV7MFQpbycp94Klk5Z0fLZIFo%3D%2F1200x628%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNOIC33HGAJFMDE3LYIJLZP6UOQ.jpg&h=c314e79e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍可兒離奇命案當年轟動全球。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mmAB8cmKTb5aScwIEdYDNu5bE6c=/205x246/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/22APAKANKRE7XAKUBF52VIYFBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmmAB8cmKTb5aScwIEdYDNu5bE6c%3D%2F205x246%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F22APAKANKRE7XAKUBF52VIYFBU.jpg&h=93b0d1ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關於藍可兒的Netflix紀錄片《Crime Scene: The Vanishing at The Cecil Hotel》下月全球上架。<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》英文版免費試睇：了解更多<br />\n<br />\n英文版已登錄《蘋果》App，立即下載/ 更新：iOS / Android<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n支持蘋果深度報道，深入社區，踢爆權貴，即Like蘋果專題及調查組FB專頁！"}]}